## Note on TLS Certs

New `*.app.sparkmojo.com` subdomains initially served self-signed certs.
Traefik ACME will issue Let's Encrypt certs automatically (may take a few minutes).
The Frappe Desk subdomains (admin, internal, willow) already have valid certs.

## Note on Traefik Version

Traefik v3.5.2 is running. The INFRA-TRAEFIK.md spec used Traefik v2 HostRegexp
syntax (`{name:pattern}`), which was corrected to Traefik v3 raw regex syntax
(`^[a-z0-9-]+\.app\.sparkmojo\.com$`).
